commit message: Add test project.
Add result parser test.
Add more parser tests.
Updated from 'DeliciousDroid' to 'PinDroid'
Switched to cursor based auto complete, also added count to view.
Beginnings of multiple account support.
Fix global tag search.
Mostly working.
Rebase cleanup.
Account changes within list views happen immediately.
Removed most fragment -> base activity references.
Removed settings from FragmentBaseActivity.
Multiple accounts not supported on < v14.

Fix searching.

- Searching from within app should be context sensitive with respect to the account currently selected.
- Searching from the global quick search box should search all accounts.
Account specific small widget.
Fix search button on widgets.
Remove choose account menu option from several activities.
Tag shortcuts are now account specific.
Fix changing account after viewing bookmark list filtered by tag.
Cleanup.
Fix bookmark list on phone.
Fix username call in auto complete.
Add bookmark properly respects chosen account.
Update gitignore to ignore test project generated files.
Add configuration for account specific large widget.
Fix some bugs with view bookmark, opening read and web views and backing out quickly would cause a FC.
Some minor refactoring and clean up.
Fix bug with bookmark search suggestion selection.
Changed unread icons, old unread icon is now note icon.
Add note button option for 1x1 widget.
Fix fc caused by outofmemoryerror.
Clear bookmark view when switching accounts.
Fix account and time not showing on tablet bookmark view.
Canceling account chooser should not finish activity.
Merging multiple account support.

Merge pull request #9 from jslag/master

update .project file
Change bookmark serialization to parcel based.
Fix adding bookmarks from share not setting account.
Fix several issues with account selection and adding bookmarks.
Fix global search suggestion inconsistencies.
Fix global search suggestion title.
Fix username in notes and tags.
Adjust some sizes, add action bar subtitle if multiple accounts.
Fix account not being switchable after entering app through widget.
Fix add bookmark fc after entering from widget.
Adjust some sizes and layouts of view bookmark screen.
Hide tags and notes on view bookmark screen if none in bookmark.
Add unread icon to view bookmark screen.
Use correct titles for recent and network bookmarks.
Switch read view back to instapaper.
Save username if activity is unloaded from memory.
Add support for dashclock widget extension.
Separate intent and content authorities.
Add dashclock extension to main app.
Cleanup.
Add bookmark screen shouldn't ask for account when sharing a url from within the app.
Fix read default view from search suggestions.
Global search suggestions indicate what account the suggestion is for.
Only print account name in global search suggestions if there is more than 1 account.
Changed automatic sync text.
Lint cleanup.
Change uri pattern for querying individual bookmarks and notes.
Fixed editing bookmarks and adding bookmark from feed for tablets.
Added null check to bookmarkFrag instance check.
Currently selected account should be selected by default in account picker.
Don't spawn multiple account pickers after orientation changes.
Don't need to kill account picker when selected from menu.
Add setting to always use browser to open web links.
Change capitalization of settings items to match Google's standards.
Read later share now asks for account properly.
Finish view bookmark activity when bookmark is deleted.
Set version number.
Merge branch 'development'
